1396
01:16:17,673 --> 01:16:19,640
[GENTLE MUSIC]

1397
01:16:25,681 --> 01:16:26,613
[GRUNTS]

1398
01:16:26,649 --> 01:16:29,616
[GENTLE MUSIC]

1399
01:16:29,652 --> 01:16:32,619
[CLANKING]

1400
01:16:32,655 --> 01:16:35,255
[GRUNTS]

1401
01:16:45,601 --> 01:16:47,267
Magearna, we're here.

1402
01:16:52,308 --> 01:16:54,508
[ALL GASP]

1403
01:16:54,543 --> 01:16:58,278
MEOWTH: It's heart
is still broken.

1404
01:16:58,314 --> 01:17:00,447
Sure it can move
and all that stuff.

1405
01:17:00,482 --> 01:17:07,421
But now, Magearna's voice,
I can't hear it at all.

1406
01:17:07,456 --> 01:17:09,423
[GRUNTS]

1407
01:17:11,660 --> 01:17:13,427
[ALL SIGH]

1408
01:17:13,495 --> 01:17:14,428
[CLANKING]

1409
01:17:14,463 --> 01:17:15,228
[ALL GASPING]

1410
01:17:21,437 --> 01:17:22,436
Oh, no.

1411
01:17:22,471 --> 01:17:27,107
The fortress is set to
fall onto Nebel Plateau.

1412
01:17:27,142 --> 01:17:28,342
Can it be stopped?

1413
01:17:28,377 --> 01:17:31,411
It can't it looks like
the control system is out.

1414
01:17:31,447 --> 01:17:35,048
All because of Alva.

1415
01:17:35,084 --> 01:17:37,084
And even if we were
able to escape--

1416
01:17:49,498 --> 01:17:52,065
Isn't there any way at all?

1417
01:17:52,101 --> 01:17:53,467
We can't change course.

1418
01:17:53,502 --> 01:17:56,002
The only way would be
to explode the fortress

1419
01:17:56,038 --> 01:17:58,405
into a pile of dust.

1420
01:17:58,440 --> 01:18:02,109
Explosions are my specialty.

1421
01:18:02,144 --> 01:18:03,276
Hold on.

1422
01:18:03,312 --> 01:18:04,144
You're out of water.

1423
01:18:07,349 --> 01:18:12,285
Part of the fortress runs on
steam so it has water tanks.

1424
01:18:12,321 --> 01:18:14,988
Volcanion, I'll take you there.

1425
01:18:15,023 --> 01:18:16,990
Please do.

1426
01:18:17,025 --> 01:18:20,060
Everybody, wait on my
sister's flying machine.

1427
01:18:20,095 --> 01:18:21,328
I'm going with you.

1428
01:18:21,363 --> 01:18:22,329
Pika ka.

1429
01:18:28,070 --> 01:18:29,035
Over here!

1430
01:18:32,174 --> 01:18:33,974
I can smell water.

1431
01:18:36,412 --> 01:18:38,345
[GROANING]

1432
01:18:40,048 --> 01:18:43,016
This thing is really stuck.

1433
01:18:43,051 --> 01:18:44,050
I've got it.

1434
01:18:44,086 --> 01:18:45,452
Go for it, Pikachu.

1435
01:18:45,487 --> 01:18:46,420
Irontail!

1436
01:18:46,455 --> 01:18:48,054
Pika!

1437
01:18:48,090 --> 01:18:49,289
Ah, pika!

1438
01:18:54,329 --> 01:18:55,162
Hey, thanks.

1439
01:18:55,197 --> 01:18:57,364
[GROANING]

1440
01:19:02,070 --> 01:19:03,036
It's moving.

1441
01:19:10,078 --> 01:19:11,077
All right.

1442
01:19:11,113 --> 01:19:12,045
Yeah!

1443
01:19:27,095 --> 01:19:28,962
Excuse me.

1444
01:19:28,997 --> 01:19:30,397
You said your name
was Ash, right?

1445
01:19:30,432 --> 01:19:31,965
That's right.

1446
01:19:32,000 --> 01:19:34,334
I've been acting
like such a fool,

1447
01:19:34,369 --> 01:19:38,104
spending so long shutting
myself up in my lab.

1448
01:19:38,140 --> 01:19:44,077
That's why Alva had such an
easy time tricking me that way.

1449
01:19:44,112 --> 01:19:46,346
You know what I think?

1450
01:19:46,381 --> 01:19:50,050
You should head out on your
own journey with a Pokemon.

1451
01:19:50,085 --> 01:19:51,051
Huh?

1452
01:19:51,086 --> 01:19:52,052
Mm-hmm.

1453
01:19:52,087 --> 01:19:54,054
Pika te.

1454
01:19:54,089 --> 01:19:55,021
[CRASH]

1455
01:19:55,057 --> 01:19:56,022
[GASPS]

1456
01:20:06,134 --> 01:20:07,100
[CRASH]

1457
01:20:16,245 --> 01:20:18,211
[PANTING]

1458
01:20:22,484 --> 01:20:23,583
Volcanion?

1459
01:20:23,619 --> 01:20:28,154
Say, perhaps I should create
an explosion right here.

1460
01:20:28,190 --> 01:20:30,156
ASH: It is the center
of the fortress

1461
01:20:30,192 --> 01:20:32,058
so I do think it
would be effective.

1462
01:20:32,094 --> 01:20:34,427
But then you won't
be able to escape.

1463
01:20:34,463 --> 01:20:36,162
Vita vio.

1464
01:20:36,198 --> 01:20:38,198
Yeah, that's the truth.

1465
01:20:38,233 --> 01:20:41,334
You said you're powerful enough
to level a mountain, right?

1466
01:20:41,370 --> 01:20:44,137
So why not follow the plan
and blow it up from outside?

1467
01:20:44,172 --> 01:20:45,505
Hmm.

1468
01:20:45,541 --> 01:20:47,507
Agreed.

1469
01:20:47,543 --> 01:20:49,175
We should all go back together.

1470
01:20:49,211 --> 01:20:50,143
Yeah.

1471
01:20:50,178 --> 01:20:51,077
Pika!

1472
01:20:51,113 --> 01:20:53,079
[CRASH]

1473
01:20:53,115 --> 01:20:54,047
Let's hurry.

1474
01:21:01,256 --> 01:21:02,155
[CRASH]

1475
01:21:02,190 --> 01:21:03,156
[ALL GASP]

1476
01:21:16,505 --> 01:21:18,171
OK, Volcanion.

1477
01:21:18,206 --> 01:21:19,372
Go get them!

1478
01:21:19,408 --> 01:21:20,206
[GRUNTS]

1479
01:21:31,286 --> 01:21:33,219
Get on board after the blast.

1480
01:21:33,255 --> 01:21:35,021
All right.

1481
01:21:35,057 --> 01:21:36,356
Just go!

1482
01:21:36,391 --> 01:21:38,358
[ALL MOANING]

1483
01:21:42,431 --> 01:21:43,363
CHYMIA: Volcanion!

1484
01:21:49,404 --> 01:21:50,236
No!

1485
01:21:50,272 --> 01:21:52,038
You can't do that!

1486
01:21:57,279 --> 01:21:58,511
[GRUNTS]

1487
01:22:08,490 --> 01:22:11,458
Well, I'm going
out with a bang.

1488
01:22:11,493 --> 01:22:13,093
Time to blast!

1489
01:22:22,504 --> 01:22:27,173
Magearna, I couldn't
protect you.

1490
01:22:27,209 --> 01:22:29,142
Forgive me.

1491
01:22:29,177 --> 01:22:32,178
[ROARING]

1492
01:22:39,121 --> 01:22:40,253
Volcanion.

1493
01:22:40,288 --> 01:22:43,023
[HIGH PITCHED SOUND]

1494
01:22:49,164 --> 01:22:52,098
[EXPLOSION]

1495
01:23:11,453 --> 01:23:14,087
You lied to us.

1496
01:23:14,122 --> 01:23:17,090
You said we'd all
go back together!

1497
01:23:17,125 --> 01:23:18,258
Heego bego.

1498
01:23:42,150 --> 01:23:44,217
Magearna?

1499
01:23:44,252 --> 01:23:47,020
The Nebel Plateau
Pokemon are safe.

1500
01:23:47,055 --> 01:23:50,190
Volcanion protected them.

1501
01:23:50,225 --> 01:23:52,292
I wish you could
hear what I'm saying.

1502
01:23:52,327 --> 01:23:55,095
[GENTLE MUSIC]

1503
01:24:00,102 --> 01:24:02,068
[ALL WHIMPERING]

1504
01:24:05,307 --> 01:24:07,073
[PURRING]

1505
01:24:11,313 --> 01:24:13,079
[CRYING]

1506
01:24:13,115 --> 01:24:15,248
[GASPS]

1507
01:24:15,283 --> 01:24:18,051
[ALL WHIMPERING]

1508
01:24:21,289 --> 01:24:23,256
[GASPING]

1509
01:24:30,132 --> 01:24:31,097
[ALL EXCLAIMING]

1510
01:24:31,133 --> 01:24:32,298
Look at the mist.

1511
01:24:32,334 --> 01:24:33,299
[GENTLE MUSIC]

1512
01:24:40,275 --> 01:24:41,241
[ALL EXCLAIMING]

1513
01:24:50,085 --> 01:24:51,050
[ALL EXCLAIMING]

1514
01:24:55,090 --> 01:24:56,055
[ALL EXCLAIMING]

1515
01:25:15,110 --> 01:25:17,043
[BEEPING]

1516
01:25:21,049 --> 01:25:22,215
[GRUNTING]

1517
01:25:22,250 --> 01:25:24,217
[BEEPING]

1518
01:25:24,252 --> 01:25:26,219
[ALL EXCLAIMING]

1519
01:25:27,222 --> 01:25:28,988
Magearna.

1520
01:25:29,024 --> 01:25:31,991
[BEEPING]

1521
01:25:38,166 --> 01:25:40,166
Chesnah.

1522
01:25:40,202 --> 01:25:41,134
Chesnah.

1523
01:25:45,340 --> 01:25:46,306
[GRUNTING]

1524
01:25:46,341 --> 01:25:48,308
[BEEPING]

1525
