[GRUNTS]

1526
01:25:53,114 --> 01:25:55,281
[GROANS]

1527
01:25:55,317 --> 01:25:58,251
[ALL GASP]

1528
01:25:58,286 --> 01:26:00,320
Volcanion, hang in there.

1529
01:26:02,290 --> 01:26:03,223
Volcanion?

1530
01:26:07,462 --> 01:26:09,095
Oh.

1531
01:26:09,130 --> 01:26:11,064
Pika.

1532
01:26:11,099 --> 01:26:14,000
[WHIMPERING]

1533
01:26:25,313 --> 01:26:26,212
[GASPS]

1534
01:26:26,248 --> 01:26:28,982
[SQUEAKING]

1535
01:26:29,017 --> 01:26:31,317
[GASPING]

1536
01:26:33,221 --> 01:26:35,054
[SNEEZES]

1537
01:26:35,090 --> 01:26:37,156
[POKEMON SCREAM]

1538
01:26:40,328 --> 01:26:42,462
I told you not to do that.

1539
01:26:42,497 --> 01:26:45,064
[POKEMON SQUEAKING]

1540
01:26:47,068 --> 01:26:50,136
You, you're still here?

1541
01:26:50,171 --> 01:26:53,239
I said I want to
protect Pokemon, right?

1542
01:26:53,275 --> 01:26:55,241
I would never tell a lie.

1543
01:26:55,277 --> 01:26:57,043
Be davi ya!

1544
01:26:57,078 --> 01:27:01,948
[CHUCKLES] All of you.

1545
01:27:01,983 --> 01:27:03,182
You know what?

1546
01:27:03,218 --> 01:27:05,118
Huh?

1547
01:27:05,153 --> 01:27:09,322
I'm going to make you all
honorary Nebel Plateau Pokemon.

1548
01:27:09,357 --> 01:27:11,190
Honorary Pokemon.

1549
01:27:11,226 --> 01:27:13,993
Hey, I think that
sounds really cool.

1550
01:27:14,029 --> 01:27:17,263
Yeah, I want to be one!

1551
01:27:17,299 --> 01:27:19,198
Yeah, right, Squishy?

1552
01:27:19,234 --> 01:27:20,366
Mm-hmm.

1553
01:27:20,402 --> 01:27:22,335
Well, I'm happy to accept.

1554
01:27:22,370 --> 01:27:24,003
It's a real honor.

1555
01:27:24,039 --> 01:27:25,371
[ALL LAUGHING]

1556
01:27:33,315 --> 01:27:35,281
Hey, electric nuisance.

1557
01:27:35,317 --> 01:27:36,382
Pika.

1558
01:27:36,418 --> 01:27:39,152
Your friend, Ash,
he always seems to be

1559
01:27:39,187 --> 01:27:41,220
getting himself into trouble.

1560
01:27:41,256 --> 01:27:42,355
Pika?

1561
01:27:42,390 --> 01:27:46,359
Take extra good care of him.

1562
01:27:46,394 --> 01:27:49,162
Pika, me gatsu.

1563
01:27:49,197 --> 01:27:50,396
[LAUGHS]

1564
01:28:11,186 --> 01:28:14,153
