1565
01:28:25,200 --> 01:28:28,201
WOMAN (SINGING):
One of a kind, forged

1566
01:28:28,236 --> 01:28:37,276
of steel from a beautiful
night with a mighty heart,

1567
01:28:37,312 --> 01:28:42,248
drove men apart.

1568
01:28:42,283 --> 01:28:49,422
Forgotten plain, where
only the damaged remain,

1569
01:28:49,457 --> 01:28:53,059
that's where I found my destiny.

1570
01:28:57,365 --> 01:29:06,406
One more lost refugee, come
with me, feel my soul-heart.

1571
01:29:06,441 --> 01:29:10,410
If you've been
seeking a new start,

1572
01:29:10,445 --> 01:29:19,419
let me be your guiding light
till the end of the night.

1573
01:29:19,454 --> 01:29:24,090
Close your eyes,
know my soul-heart,

1574
01:29:24,125 --> 01:29:28,127
keeping watch over the rampart.

1575
01:29:28,163 --> 01:29:34,133
Let me be your
shining star, leading

1576
01:29:34,169 --> 01:29:42,241
voice from afar from whoever
you were to whoever you are.

1577
01:29:45,213 --> 01:29:49,115
Feel my soul-heart now.

1578
01:29:52,320 --> 01:29:55,088
Dry all your tears.

1579
01:29:55,123 --> 01:30:00,393
I've returned after so many
years Let the creatures

1580
01:30:00,428 --> 01:30:05,364
I cherish flourish so now.

1581
01:30:08,403 --> 01:30:12,138
This is my vow.

1582
01:30:12,173 --> 01:30:16,275
Know forever my soul-heart.

1583
01:30:16,311 --> 01:30:25,318
Anyone seeking a new start,
let me be your guiding light

1584
01:30:25,353 --> 01:30:30,423
till the end of the night.

1585
